text: Zemplén may refer to: * Zemplén County, a historical region of the Kingdom of Hungary * the part of the historical region in present-day Hungary, now part of the Borsod-Abaúj-Zemplén county * Géza Zemplén, Hungarian chemist ==See also== *Borsod-Abaúj-Zemplén *Zemplén Mountains (in Hungary) *Zemplín (disambiguation)
title: Zemplén
